Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二得二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二二得四
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三得六
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二四得八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二五得十
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二六得十二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二七得十四
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二八得…十六
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二九得…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二九得…十八
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是行人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常的累
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼誠實  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家為了我那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得試著更加努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近行人常常一人外出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為在學校裡做老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼感覺行人會在我眼前消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
